Rule Your Web Empire: 
Ever dreamed of hosting your own website? Termux makes it a reality! Set up a web server [ Lighttpd, Nginx

, Apache], manage files, and even run custom web applications. Your phone becomes your personal server, ready to serve content to the world. Talk about power in your pocket!
